[{"id":"VR000569","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">Which of the following statements about the power series <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"the sum, from n equals 0, to infinity, of, n factorial times x raised to the 2 n power \"><math alttext=\"the sum, from n equals 0, to infinity, of, n factorial times x raised to the 2 n power \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle displaystyle=\"true\"><mrow><mrow><munderover><mo>∑</mo><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow><mrow><mi>∞</mi></mrow></munderover><mrow><mi>n</mi><mo>!</mo><msup><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn><mi>n</mi></mrow></msup></mrow></mrow></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is true?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VR000569_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series does not converge for any real number <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series converges for <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x equals 0 \"><math alttext=\"x equals 0 \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> only.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series converges on the interval <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"negative 1 is less than x, which is less than 1 \"><math alttext=\"negative 1 is less than x, which is less than 1 \" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mrow><mo>−</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow><mo>&lt;</mo><mi>x</mi><mo>&lt;</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> only.</p>","<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The series converges for all real numbers <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>.</p>"],"answer":1}]